    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a dependable choice for its next owner. The exterior is overall very clean, though it does have some minor surface wear and a few faint scratches typical of regular use. Inside, the cabin is well-kept with minimal signs of wear on the upholstery and all electronic features functioning as intended. Mechanically, the car runs smoothly and has a documented service history, ensuring it is ready for the road without immediate concerns. It offers a great balance of reliability and value for anyone seeking a quality pre-owned vehicle.",
