    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle of superlative caliber, this specimen represents the absolute pinnacle of automotive preservation. Maintained to an uncompromising standard, the exterior retains its factory luster, while the interior remains in showroom-grade condition, devoid of wear or imperfection. Every mechanical system has been subjected to a rigorous evaluation to ensure performance remains at its peak. This is an investment-grade offering for the individual who demands nothing less than mechanical and aesthetic perfection.",
