    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-grade specimen that satisfies the most exacting standards. The exterior is finished in a deep metallic paint that remains entirely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or road rash, having been protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating and stored in a climate-controlled garage. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the hand-stitched leather bolsters show no signs of compression or wear, the carpets are pristine, and the interior retains its original factory scent. Every switch, dial, and digital display operates with crisp, tactile precision. Mechanically, this vehicle is flawless, backed by a comprehensive service portfolio documenting every fluid change and inspection performed ahead of schedule at authorized centers. It has never seen rain or snow, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. This sale includes the full set of original keys, all owner's manuals, and a thick folder of maintenance provenance. For the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the one.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
